---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Επικοινωνία" active="contact">

<main class="pt-32 pb-24 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
  <!-- Header Section -->
  <header class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
      <div class="h-px w-12 bg-primary"></div>
      <span class="text-primary font-black text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Get in Touch</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black italic mb-8 uppercase leading-tight">
      ΕΠΙΚΟΙΝΩΝΗΣΤΕ <br class="hidden sm:block"/> <span class="text-primary">ΜΑΖΙ ΜΑΣ</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
      Είμαστε εδώ για να συζητήσουμε τις τεχνικές σας ανάγκες και να προσφέρουμε τις κατάλληλες λύσεις.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-24">
    <!-- Contact Info -->
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <div class="bg-surface p-8 sm:p-12 border border-border/50">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40 mb-10">Στοιχεία Επικοινωνίας</h3>
        <div class="space-y-10">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">location_on</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60 mb-2">Διεύθυνση</p>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-black text-white group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Βιομηχανική Περιοχή Ασπροπύργου,<br/>Θέση Δύο Πεύκα, 19300</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">call</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60 mb-2">Τηλέφωνο</p>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-black text-white group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">+30 210 000 0000</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">mail</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60 mb-2">Email</p>
              <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-black text-white group-hover:text-primary transition-colors text-wrap break-all">info@elite-industrial.gr</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-primary p-8 sm:p-12 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white italic mb-6 uppercase">Technical Support</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Για επείγουσες τεχνικές βλάβες και υποστήριξη 24/7, παρακαλούμε καλέστε στην γραμμή άμεσης βοήθειας.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+302100000001" class="inline-block bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/90 transition-all">
            +30 210 000 0001
          </a>
        </div>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute -right-8 -bottom-8 text-[120px] sm:text-[160px] text-white/10 rotate-12">engineering</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Form -->
    <div class="bg-surface p-8 sm:p-12 border border-border/50 relative">
      <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 sm:-top-6 sm:-right-6 w-16 h-16 sm:w-24 sm:h-24 border-t-4 border-r-4 border-primary"></div>
      <form class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60">Ονοματεπώνυμο</label>
            <input type="text" class="w-full bg-background border border-border/50 px-4 py-4 text-white focus:border-primary outline-none transition-colors" />
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60">Email</label>
            <input type="email" class="w-full bg-background border border-border/50 px-4 py-4 text-white focus:border-primary outline-none transition-colors" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <label class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60">Θέμα</label>
          <input type="text" class="w-full bg-background border border-border/50 px-4 py-4 text-white focus:border-primary outline-none transition-colors" />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <label class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60">Μήνυμα</label>
          <textarea rows="6" class="w-full bg-background border border-border/50 px-4 py-4 text-white focus:border-primary outline-none transition-colors"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button class="w-full bg-primary text-white py-5 sm:py-6 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-primary-hover transition-all">
          Αποστολή Μηνύματος
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

</Layout>
